{"tid":2324280,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"只要你夠惡Facebook就會買你怕","createTime":"2020-12-13T22:48:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-14T05:09:59.000Z","uid":319328,"like":35,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"493cc208a98d3c0880ed9d7ca6d40cc0c91d4cb7","tid":2324280,"uid":319328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T22:48:07.000Z","msg":"因為班印度佬夠惡，Facebook 都要買佢怕唔敢剷佢account。<br />\n<br />\n唔好再同我講咩鼓吹仇恨、行為不當⋯⋯ 全部都係藉口。喺香港就大大聲，一見到班惡棍就笠晒水，根本就係欺善怕惡，用藉口包裝自己嘅仆街公司。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xQmbmqq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxQmbmqq.png&h=38777406&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.wsj.com/articles/in-india-facebook-fears-crackdown-on-hate-groups-could-backfire-on-its-staff-11607871600?st=bdf4ekbxzhgqdu8&amp;reflink=article_copyURL_share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Farticles%2Fin-india-facebook-fears-crackdown-on-hate-groups-could-backfire-on-its-staff-11607871600%3Fst%3Dbdf4ekbxzhgqdu8%26reflink%3Darticle_copyURL_share&d=WHMLQMiyWmfm849WKe725DsyqOHkMMjDRpVYVMaq87A%3D&h=d0e54b19\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.wsj.com/articles/in-india-facebook-fears-crackdown-on-hate-groups-could-backfire-on-its-staff-11607871600?st=bdf4ekbxzhgqdu8&amp;reflink=article_copyURL_share</a>"},{"pid":"f6de87541f8ad6c00fa103dabe2f4b793bf530e8","tid":2324280,"uid":228894,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T22:58:15.000Z","msg":"其實都係睇市場人口"},{"pid":"08850f9660651d146035e033df50606d680b2c84","tid":2324280,"uid":283741,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T23:03:09.000Z","msg":"根本和理非只會益咗全無章法嘅支那狗，要反共必須軍事化"},{"pid":"1fd5a8c2bcd0a9768175ba9f9db7280253706a10","tid":2324280,"uid":123774,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T23:08:25.000Z","msg":"Facebook當印度係一個市場睇<br />\n<br />\n同樣地香港Facebook背後支那人 <br />\n根本唔介意犧牲香港市場為人民幣而活"},{"pid":"17638285e023